{"tid":947150,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"落機唔見手機 有冇人可以幫手","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T10:30:14.000Z","uid":58547,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f49579ceb3a6ad6aad48e13190e0f7b69900d7b","tid":947150,"uid":58547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC開<br />\n<br />\n我今日搭UO 33由羽田番香港<br />\n拎行李先發現唔見咗手機 <br />\n已經即時同地勤講<br />\n佢話搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我一直都有開Find my iPhone嘅<br />\n喺香港Find my iPhone 冇反應因爲張卡係日本卡<br />\n直至岩岩我喺手機見到我手機喺37分鐘之前去左<span style=\"font-size: large;\">福岡</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTimeline係<br />\n5點落機, 地勤話6點做清潔<br />\n咁岩有班UO 600由香港飛往福岡7:40起, 11:52到<br />\n即係香港時間10:52到<br />\n而我部手機喺12:00香港時間顯示喺福岡<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知係我自己唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係入面真係有好多好多好重要嘅相 希望有人可以幫到我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbyD2bj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbyD2bj.png&h=848024d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f41af8b712c0842f5861639665f2c5a69d077031","tid":947150,"uid":148551,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"點解你會覺得有人幫到你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f960cde0c9db5882a258a24031b8e19518b00d","tid":947150,"uid":61543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"你想連燈仔點幫你"},{"pid":"2718c2e1d7d1ea06737a7aa0fb4b03c97246b207","tid":947150,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"你上lijpg問啦"},{"pid":"f2dd87e80254734e6d90b3fa6b643d2603b7cd95","tid":947150,"uid":58547,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"50f960cde0c9db5882a258a24031b8e19518b00d","tid":947150,"uid":61543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"你想連燈仔點幫你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"其實我係度諗 究竟會唔會係第一程機既時間咁岩收到signal定係佢真係喺日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4217ef2dbdb98fcfdf273e63f5d54e5aae83accd","tid":947150,"uid":109383,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UyPsbYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUyPsbYO.png&h=160ff285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5478126a484ca643c14b332bffad5d64347b91f1","tid":947150,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"又好多珍貴相，又係無開icloud backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8954d34b4196ccda6111315ca2c8de18865659","tid":947150,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"可能部手機跟飛機又飛返去日本了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65977f987587512af5463d444016e9f640d0fa32","tid":947150,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5478126a484ca643c14b332bffad5d64347b91f1","tid":947150,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T08:26:52.000Z","msg":"又好多珍貴相，又係無開icloud backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"個個唔見電話post都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}